body_html:
I'm seeing a test failure on MacOS that may be related--

tensorflow/contrib/lite/profiling/profiler_test.cc:34
The difference between expected_ms and duration_ms is 10.062999999999988, which exceeds eps_ms, where
expected_ms evaluates to 500,
duration_ms evaluates to 510.06299999999999, and
eps_ms evaluates to 10.

@skambha would that be expected from your changes? @shashishekhar , can you comment as the author of that test?

body:
I'm seeing a test failure on MacOS that may be related-- 

```
tensorflow/contrib/lite/profiling/profiler_test.cc:34
The difference between expected_ms and duration_ms is 10.062999999999988, which exceeds eps_ms, where
expected_ms evaluates to 500,
duration_ms evaluates to 510.06299999999999, and
eps_ms evaluates to 10.
```
@skambha would that be expected from your changes? @shashishekhar , can you comment as the author of that test?
